url: "https://github.com/searchsim-org/nuggetindex"
abstract: >
  nuggetindex is a time-aware, conflict-aware fact retrieval sidecar
  for RAG stacks. It stores atomic facts as governed records with
  validity intervals, lifecycle states (Active / Deprecated /
  Contested), and provenance, and exposes a `nuggetindex resolve`
  CLI for human-in-the-loop adjudication of source disagreements.
  Drop-in adapters for LangChain, LlamaIndex, and Haystack.
keywords:
  - rag
  - retrieval
  - temporal-ir
  - nugget-evaluation
  - fact-maintenance
